statements: SELECT * FROM fingerprint_images;
SELECT image_id, user_id FROM fingerprint_images WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT image_id, capture_time FROM fingerprint_images ORDER BY capture_time DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id FROM fingerprint_images;
SELECT AVG(image_id) as average_image_id FROM fingerprint_images;
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_images WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY capture_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT image_id, capture_time, user_id FROM fingerprint_images WHERE user_id = 2 ORDER BY capture_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_images WHERE user_id = 3 AND capture_time > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY capture_time ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT image_id, image_data FROM fingerprint_images WHERE user_id = 4 AND image_id BETWEEN 100 AND 200;
SELECT image_id, user_id, capture_time FROM fingerprint_images WHERE user_id = 5 AND capture_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2023-01-01' ORDER BY capture_time DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_images WHERE user_id = 1234;
SELECT id, user_id FROM fingerprint_images WHERE id > 100 AND uploaded_at > '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT id, image_data, uploaded_at FROM fingerprint_images WHERE uploaded_at BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-06-30 23:59:59';
SELECT * FROM biometric_data WHERE user_id = 5678 ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS num_fingerprints FROM fingerprint_images GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;
SELECT id, image_data, user_id, uploaded_at FROM fingerprint_images WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY uploaded_at DESC;
SELECT image_data, user_id FROM fingerprint_images WHERE uploaded_at > '2021-01-01';
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) FROM fingerprint_images GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id FROM fingerprint_images ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT id, fingerprint_template FROM biometric_data WHERE user_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM Users;
SELECT user_id, username FROM Users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Identification;
SELECT username, password_hash FROM Users WHERE username = 'john_doe';
SELECT fingerprint_id, fingerprint_data FROM FingerprintImages ORDER BY fingerprint_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM FingerprintImages WHERE id = 1;
SELECT user_id, username FROM Users ORDER BY username DESC;
SELECT fingerprint_id, user_id, timestamp FROM Identification WHERE fingerprint_id = 2 ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_identifications FROM Identification WHERE user_id = 100;
SELECT username, fingerprint_data FROM Users INNER JOIN FingerprintImages ON Users.user_id = FingerprintImages.id;
SELECT * FROM fingerprints ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, image FROM fingerprints WHERE person_id = 5;
SELECT id, name, age FROM persons WHERE age > 30 AND gender = 'Male';
SELECT fingerprint_id, person_id, record_type FROM fingerprint_records WHERE record_type = 'Access';
SELECT * FROM fingerprint_logs ORDER BY log_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM persons WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT id, name, age FROM persons WHERE gender = 'Male' ORDER BY age;

SELECT fingerprints.person_id, COUNT(fingerprints.id) AS num_fingerprints FROM fingerprints JOIN fingerprint_records ON fingerprints.id = fingerprint_records.fingerprint_id GROUP BY fingerprints.person_id;

SELECT fingerprints.person_id, persons.name, COUNT(fingerprint_records.id) AS num_records FROM fingerprints JOIN fingerprint_records ON fingerprints.id = fingerprint_records.fingerprint_id JOIN persons ON fingerprints.person_id = persons.id GROUP BY fingerprints.person_id, persons.name;

SELECT fingerprint_logs.action, fingerprint_logs.log_time, persons.name FROM fingerprint_logs JOIN fingerprints ON fingerprint_logs.fingerprint_id = fingerprints.id JOIN persons ON fingerprints.person_id = persons.id ORDER BY fingerprint_logs.log_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM Users;
SELECT user_id, username FROM Users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM AccessLogs ORDER BY access_time DESC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(log_id) AS log_count FROM AccessLogs GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT Users.username, MatchingResults.match_score FROM Users INNER JOIN MatchingResults ON Users.user_id = MatchingResults.user_id;
SELECT * FROM Users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT username FROM Users WHERE username LIKE 'admin%';
SELECT user_id, username FROM Users WHERE user_id > 10 ORDER BY username DESC;
SELECT U.username, F.image FROM Users U JOIN FingerprintImages F ON U.user_id = F.fingerprint_id;

SELECT U.username, A.access_time, M.match_score FROM Users U JOIN AccessLogs A ON U.user_id = A.user_id JOIN MatchingResults M ON U.user_id = M.user_id WHERE M.match_score > 0.8 ORDER BY A.access_time DESC;
